data.text:
1933–present, age 89, born tokyo, japan. yoko, also known as yoko ono lennon is a japanese multimedia artist, singer, songwriter and peace activist. she and her family moved to new york in 1953. 1969 she married to john lennon of the beatles.

black conté pencil drawing 20x27 inch (51x69 cm) approx.
